keyMappings:
map [b previousTab
map ]b nextTab
map <a-f> LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab
unmap J
unmap K
map J nextTab
map K previousTab
unmap zH
unmap zL
map zh scrollToLeft
map zl scrollToRight
unmap ^
map <c-6> visitPreviousTab
unmap g0
unmap g$
map <space>1 firstTab
map <space>0 lastTab
map ; passNextKey
map <a-F> LinkHints.activateModeWithQueue
map <a-d> LinkHints.activateModeToDownloadLink
map R reload hard
